        </header>
        <main class="px-3">

            <p class="lead"> Welcome to NepCamp! <br> Jump right in and explore our popular campgrounds,dating,picnic
                spots. <br>
                Feel free to share some of your own and comment on others!</p>
            <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary font-weight-bold border-white bg-white"
                id='view'>View
                Campgrounds</a>
        </main>

        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy; 2021 </p>
        </footer>


    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
